# Customer Segmentation Analysis

## Objective
To segment customers into different groups based on their purchasing behavior.

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Scikit-learn (K-Means Clustering)

## Steps Performed
- Data Cleaning
- Feature Selection
- Applying K-Means Algorithm
- Cluster Visualization

## Key Insights
- Customers were divided into different spending groups.
- High-value customers were identified.
- Business can target each segment differently.

## Conclusion
Customer segmentation helps businesses improve marketing strategies and increase revenue.
